### 주문 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 5509426484088832,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 5509441608749056,
      "quantity": 10
    }
  ],
    "deliveryAddress": {
      "recipientName": "홍길동",
      "ordererEmail": "gildong@example.com",
      "zipCode": "06236",
      "addressLine1": "서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 123",
      "addressLine2": "10층 1001호",
      "city": "서울",
      "state": "KR"
  }
}

### 주문 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 전체 조회(기본: createdAt,DESC)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 키워드: "셔츠"
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?keyword=셔츠
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 키워드: 공백만(검색 비활성화되어 전체 조회)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?keyword=
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 9/1~10/7 사이 주문(양끝 포함 느낌: to는 '다음날 0시' 미만)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?from=2025-09-01&to=2025-10-07
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 하루치 (10/07 하루만)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?from=2025-10-07&to=2025-10-07
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 금액 오름차순
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?sort=totalAmount,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 2페이지(0-base), 10개씩
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

### 9월~10/7 사이 "맨투맨" 키워드, 최신순
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/orders?keyword=%EB%A7%A8%ED%88%AC%EB%A7%A8&from=2025-09-01&to=2025-10-07&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}
